         following applies:\n\
        \    \n\
        \     {ul\n\
        \           {-  If the default VPC in the target Region doesn\226\128\153t have an \
         internet gateway attached to it, the DB shard group is private.\n\
        \               \n\
        \                }\n\
        \           {-  If the default VPC in the target Region has an internet gateway attached \
         to it, the DB shard group is public.\n\
        \               \n\
        \                }\n\
